commentText:
Set a concurrency for the listener, if any._

The concurrency limits can be a "lower-upper" String, e.g. "5-10", or a simple_upper limit String, e.g. "10" (the lower limit will be 1 in this case)._

The underlying container may or may not support all features. For instance, it_may not be able to scale: in that case only the upper value is used.
